'''Chabab Atlas Khénifra''' is a [[Morocco|Moroccan]] [[football (soccer)|football]] club currently playing in the [[Botola]]. The club is located in the town of [[Khénifra]]. The club finished in the 2nd place in the [[Botola 2]] in the 2013–14 season, which led to the promotion to the first division.
