The high average in [[darts]] is the average score achieved with all three [[Dart (missile)|darts]] thrown. [[Michael van Gerwen]] is the current world record holder with a televised average of 123.40 thrown in the [[2016 Premier League Darts|2016 Premier League]] against [[Michael Smith (darts player)|Michael Smith]].
