==International career== Lam was born in Macau and moved to Hong Kong in 1993.<ref>{{cite web |title=港澳埠際賽 前港青林毅東披澳門戰衣 |url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20170901/bkn-20170901223544054-0901_00882_001.html |website=on.cc |accessdate=1 September 2017}} {{zh-hk icon}}</ref> He earned his first cap with [[Macau national football team|Macau]] on 5 September 2017 in a 2–0 loss to India.<ref>{{cite web |title=亞洲盃足球外圍賽 澳門隊零比二負印度 |url=https://www.cyberctm.com/zh_TW/news/detail/1960568#.W2CR-9VKiM9 |website=CTM |accessdate=6 September 2017}} {{zh-hk icon}}</ref>
