{{update|date=April 2017}} The '''Madagascar Davis Cup team''' represents [[Madagascar]] in [[Davis Cup]] [[tennis]] competition and are governed by the [[Fédération Malgache de Tennis]].
Madagascar currently compete in the Europe/Africa Zone of Group III. They finished 4th in Group III in [[2001 Davis Cup|2001]] and [[2002 Davis Cup|2002]].
==History== Madagascar competed in its first Davis Cup in [[1997 Davis Cup|1997]].
