'''Marcello "Chelo" Michelangel Anthony Pisas''' (born 4 September 1977 in [[Willemstad]]) is a [[Curaçao]] footballer Professional who currently plays as a [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]] for [[Centro Social Deportivo Barber]] in Netherlands Antilles First League. and the [[Netherlands Antilles national football team|Netherlands Antilles national team]].
