'''SCSV Kamal Dewaker''' is a Surinamese football club based in [[Livorno, Suriname|Livorno]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Team Profile: Kamal Dewaker|url=http://www.goalface.com/teams/kamal-dewaker/|publisher=GoalFace, Inc.|accessdate=31 July 2011}}</ref>  The club plays in the [[Hoofdklasse (Suriname)|Surinamese Hoofdklasse]], the top tier of football in the nation. The club was founded on August 15, 1941.<ref name=founding>{{cite web|title=SV Kamal Dewaker: Club History|url=http://www.weltfussballarchiv.com/Vereinsprofilnew.php?ID=10410|publisher=Weltfussballarchiv|accessdate=31 July 2011}}</ref>

